Version 2 update (5/19/10)  - Improvements for FPS

A map for the cDS (Cyber Death Squad) clan: http://www.cyberdeathsquad.com/

A combination dev textured and standard map with a quick and open upper level and a lower water cavern filled with pillars.  There are access points at both ends and in the middle as well as a couple of drop-in holes.  The lower level uses muted lighting and players at a distance will appear as dark forms.

Also, there is a spinning skull with glowing read eyes...

~~~Worm
